{"tid":641194,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《花木蘭》真人版電影將再添三名重量級華人影星","createTime":"2018-04-24T21:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T04:03:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9072b6736ca478060bf4de7e4a33cd93d4b647","tid":641194,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T21:42:48.000Z","msg":"Disney 宣布拍攝《花木蘭》真人版電影後，堅持要以會武術、外語能力與明星魅力三大原則進行試鏡，除了主角確定由劉亦菲飾演之外，根據 THR 與 Variety 報導，這部電影將再添三名重量級華人影星。<br />\n<br />\n比照選角原則，這三名演員分別是甄子丹、鞏俐以及李連杰，角色分配方面，鞏俐將演出女性反派角色，而李連杰則是飾演皇帝一角。據悉，有了鞏俐的加入之後，這部真人版電影將會與動畫劇情有所不同，並會為這部電影注入更多不同元素在裡頭。《花木蘭》真人版電影預計在 2020 年上映，屆時就讓我們一同見證他是否符合各位的期待值吧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7TJt9rID_38HDz5Z.sWtkQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com/ebeecfe6b97d7f64cdf62d208cc8b4d0/tumblr_inline_p7o2o1aD7r1t4qai9_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7TJt9rID_38HDz5Z.sWtkQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Febeecfe6b97d7f64cdf62d208cc8b4d0%2Ftumblr_inline_p7o2o1aD7r1t4qai9_1280.jpg&h=91adcb88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%9C%A8%E8%98%AD%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%88%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%87%E5%86%8D%E6%B7%BB%E4%B8%89%E5%90%8D%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F%E7%B4%9A%E8%8F%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%BD%B1%E6%98%9F-015527883.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkstylemen.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258A%25B1%25E6%259C%25A8%25E8%2598%25AD%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%2588%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2587%258F%25E7%25B4%259A%25E8%258F%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E6%2598%259F-015527883.html&d=jOwcmthtePpxluzTd%2FfiBMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=cb0f4d6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%9C%A8%E8%98%AD%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E